    "The result is a list of temporal features generated one by one according to the autoregressive decoder style.",
    "The next step is to understand how the Nx module of each approach differs (ArcRQ2) from the original design illustrated in Fig. 1.",
    "Part of the works (Li et al. 2020; Rao et al. 2022a; Meng et al. 2021; Rasmy et al. 2021; Zeng et al. 2022; Shome 2021; Darabi et al. 2020; Li et al. 2023a, b; Rao et al. 2022b; Peng et al. 2021) basically follow the encoder stage of the original transformer architecture (Fig. 1), including a final fully connected layer for classification/prediction.",
    "This layer uses activation functions such as Sigmoid (Li et al. 2020; Rao et al. 2022a) and Softmax (Florez et al. 2021; Zeng et al. 2022).",
    "Other works follow (Florez et al. 2021; Boursalie et al. 2021; Prakash et al. 2021) the decoder stage of this architecture, while the proposal in An et al. (2022) relies on both stages."
